```

#### 10. Screenshot (`screenshot`)

Capture screenshots of web pages with customizable viewport and format options.

```json
{
  "name": "screenshot",
  "arguments": {
    "url": "https://example.com",
    "width": 1280,
    "height": 800,
    "fullPage": true,
    "format": "png",
